      "body_lines": [
        "Protesting the privatization of the petroleum industry in Sri Lanka, the unions for the protection of petroleum resources protested today (22) in front of the Ministry of Energy on Ernest de Silva Mawatha near Viharamahadevi Park and handed over a memorandum to the Secretary of the Ministry."
